bedtools getfasta -fi /home/hoeps/turbo_mount_3/data/research/projects/wolfram/programs/agc/data/genomes/HG00621.2.fa -bed <(echo -e "seq66\t43754602\t49782859") > HG00621.2_region.fa

(1.2) Then use the script in scripts. Put here the chunklen; default is 10.000

cd /mnt/c/Users/Z364220/projects/mini-programs/crosshair
./scripts/align_parent_to_child.sh data/HPRC/HG01978.2_region.fa data/HPRC/HG00621.2_region.fa 10000 > HG01978.2_HG00621.2_100.paf


